docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs ¶ For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands ¶ mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout ¶ mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. C #include <stdio.h> int main ( void ) { printf ( "Hello world! \n " ); return 0 ; } C++ #include <iostream> int main ( void ) { std :: cout << "Hello world!" << std :: endl ; return 0 ; } Typescript console . log ( "Hello World" )
